# terra-siege base — Collector delivery destination + defensive turret.
# Landing pad + 4 corner lights + control tower + tower top.
# Turret cap + barrel + tip stay procedural (rotate independently with yaw).
# Local frame: +Z forward. c30 pad + c08 tower + c15 top + c05 lights.
o base

